{                                                                       \
  int current_allocation = 64;                                          \
  result = stp_malloc(current_allocation);                              \
  while (1)                                                             \
    {                                                                   \
      va_list args;                                                     \
      va_start(args, format);                                           \
      bytes = vsnprintf(result, current_allocation, format, args);      \
      va_end(args);                                                     \
      if (bytes >= 0 && bytes < current_allocation)                     \
        break;                                                          \
